# Shared NVIDIA driver/module version for GPU sandbox images.
# Referenced by:
#   - sandboxes/nvidia-gpu/Dockerfile (ARG NVIDIA_DRIVER_VERSION)
#   - tasks/scripts/vm/build-nvidia-modules.sh (NVIDIA_OPEN_VERSION)
